name: spec-led-development
description: Help maintain the local `.spec/` workspace for Spec Led Development. Use when creating or revising subject specs, aligning specs with code, tests, and guides, fixing `mix spec.verify` or `mix spec.check` findings, or checking for drift in `.spec/specs/*.spec.md`.
